5 at 610 nm, and range from ~0.10-0.40, which is consistent with\nco-formation and co-evolution of the two lobes. The hemispherical albedo of\nArrokoth varies substantially with both incidence angle and location, the\naverage hemispherical albedo at 610 nm is 0.063 +/- 0.015. The Bond albedo of\nArrokoth at 610 nm is 0.062 +/- 0.015.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 2 Mar 2020 22:21:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
