 characteristics of magnetic reconnection based\nminijets-in-a-jet model. The results, thus, suggest a strong jet-accretion-disk\ncoupling with energy input from the central source being distributed over a\nwide range in time and energy by the reconnection process depending on the\ngeometry and local physical conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2020 05:16:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-04"}
