 allows us to show that any standard well generated\ntriangulated category $\\mathcal{D}$ possesses a universal such\ncoproduct-preserving homological functor, to develop a purity theory and to\nprove that pure-injective objects always cogenerate t-structures in such\ntriangulated categories.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2020 09:30:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Jul 2020 07:58:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 8 Mar 2022 09:16:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-09"}
