\ndisabled), strong robustness, and effective localization capability even in the\nevent of sensor loss such as visual loss. The accuracy and robustness of the\nproposed method are superior to those of monocular visual inertia SLAM and\ntraditional wheel odometers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Mar 2020 13:17:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2020 07:00:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-06"}
